messages.messageBody:

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

just what you've been waiting for!

The gigantick-est sale we've ever had!

~*~ Holi-daze Studio Clearance Sale ~*~
(the only sale we've ever had...)

Get your specialty boutique hand-crafted fun stuff at 25-30% off the
regular prices! Plus tribe members get an extra 10% off!!!!!!!!!!!!

Check-out the variety of one-of-a-kind garments for kids from size 2
to size 16!! http://www.muddpies.us

Design-your-own kimono-ish wrap tops ~
~ Every size child through adult, just $25!!
~ Baby and toddler sizes, just $12!!

Add a matching or contrasting pair of wrap pants for only $20!

Super-duper special: Design your own lap quilt! Choose your color

For just $75!!!!
http://www.etsy.com/view_item.php?listing_id=504638

~ also find an assortment of trinket boxes, baby hats, doll clothes
and other gee-gaws at clearance prices ~

check out the stuff and email me if you find something interesting; be

~ customs and special orders are welcomed; if you want it for the

http://www.muddpies.etsy.com http://www.muddpies.us

Please feel free to forward this announcement to anyone in the world
you think might like to receive it.

namaste,
